    Class Description
    CopyRightAppApplicationTests  
    CopyRightApplication
    This is the main Spring Boot Application class which starts the CopyRight Application.
    CopyRightConstants
    Constants class used in the CopyRight API.
    CopyRightController
    CopyRightController is the REST Controller for the CopyRight API.
    CopyRightLambdaHandler
    This class is the entry point from AWS Lambda Function ('copyright-api-handler').
    CopyRightRequest
    This class is the Pojo that will hold the input sent from third party system / user
    CopyRightResponse
    This class is the Pojo class which includes the response String which will be populated by the CopyRightServiceImpl.class
    CopyRightService
    CopyRightService is the interface for all the functionalities that are implemented in CopyRight Application.
    CopyRightServiceImpl
    This is the core Implementation Service class for the CopyRightApplication Mainly, it reads couple of properties from application.properties and decides what the replacementToken is, and the exact words that needs to be replaced in the input String provided by the user / system
    ExceptionResponse
    Pojo class which is used by GlobalExceptionHandler class to return custom Exception Response in JSON format
    GlobalExceptionHandler
    GlobalExceptionHandler is the root Exception handler used in the CopyRight Application.
    MandatoryFieldMissingException
    Exception class for the custom Mandatory Field Missing Exception
    StringUtils
    StringUtils is a Utility class used for Basic String Operations.
    SwaggerConfig
    Swagger Configuration File for the CopyRight API which can be used for API Documentation
